headline: How Yum! Brands’ Expansion Moves Are Shaping Its 2025 Share Price Expectations
summary: Curious if Yum! Brands is a hidden gem or if you're paying too much? You're not alone. Plenty of investors are asking the same question right now. Yum! Brands' stock price has gained 10.8% year-to-date and is up 12.6% over the past year, suggesting steady optimism from the market. In the last few weeks, headlines have focused on Yum! headline: Block upgraded, Dell downgraded: Wall Street’s top analyst calls
summary: The most talked about and market moving research calls around Wall Street are now in one place. Here are today’s research calls that investors need to know, as compiled by The Fly. Top 5 Upgrades: Truist upgraded Block (XYZ) to Hold from Sell with a price target of $68, up from $67, ahead of the Investor Day on Wednesday. The risk/reward has improved following the recent pullback in the shares, and while Truist continues to worry about credit risk and the outsized growth of their Cash App Borrow
